extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em SchoolDataBase], a very basic Express website developed as a platform for Database, 

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The database has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Students:] !{data.student_count}
     
      li #[strong levels:] !{data.level_count}
      li #[strong Departments:] !{data.department_count}
      li #[strong faculties:] !{data.faculties_count}